test_large_range:
assert [6, 7, 8, 9] == [8, 9]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != 8
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 8
  Full diff:
  - [8, 9]
  + [6, 7, 8, 9]
test_even_range:
assert [12, 14, 16, 18] == [16, 18]
  At index 0 diff: 12 != 16
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 16
  Full diff:
  - [16, 18]
  + [12, 14, 16, 18]
